  "description": [
    "MILITANT MICHIGAN FARMERS PREPARING FOR DEBT STRUGGLE The following resolution is one of many passed by farmers meet ing in Ontonagon Baraga and Houghton counties Michigan This resolution was passed at a meet ing of farmers held in Snake Riv Hall Chassel Michigan Nov 14 These demands are as the comrade who sent in the report i gaid PLAIN AND CONCRETE and THE FARMERS ARE RAI LYING AROUND THEM They are not going to stop at passing this resolution This is only the beginning of the struggle for these poor farm ers They are going to put behind this resolution the weight of thousands of farmers in the ter ritory when the resolution is pre sented to the Houghton county su pervisors at their meeting in the court house on December 8 at 10 oclock in the morning The reso lution reads as follows RESOLUTION Taxes Whereas The economic crisis has developed to such a point that the farmers cannot market a large portion of their produce at all and what little can be sold brings so small returns as to hardly keep the farmers families provided with the common necessities of life At the present moment there is no"
